  <section class="ash-section ash-section--dark ash-brand">
    <div class="ash-wrap ash-brand__inner">
      <div class="ash-brand__lead">
        <p class="ash-kicker">Built by Advanced AcousticWerkes</p>
        <h2>Singapore hybrid IEM craft, since 2014.</h2>
        <p class="ash-brand__slogan">Those who listen will find the way.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="ash-brand__copy">
        <p>Advanced AcousticWerkes (AAW) designs and builds in-ear monitors in Singapore. Founded by Kevin Wang, AAW works across dynamic, balanced armature, electrostatic, planar magnetic, and hybrid platforms. Every model is shaped by physical prototyping and ear-impression feedback, not preset curves.</p>
        <p>ASH distills the hybrid approach into a seven-driver platform: a 13mm graphene dynamic woofer for bass weight, six balanced armatures for mid and treble precision, and TrueXross crossover timing that keeps all seven drivers coherent. It is built for listeners who want physical low-end authority without sacrificing vocal clarity or stage depth.</p>
        <a class="ash-btn ash-btn--ghost" href="/pages/about-us">About AAW</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

